data.title: The clonezilla from stevenshiau
data.meta_description: clonezilla is a partition or disk clone tool similar to norton ghostÂ®. it saves and restores only used blocks in hard drive. two types of clonezilla are available, clonezilla live and clonezilla se (server edition). from githubhelp.
